<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了！<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />現在是地球日期間，<delay20 />
見到<colour id="3" />然然<colour id="65535" />的話，<delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就買一些灌木幼苗好了。
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到了開花的季節，<delay8 />
綠葉上都會開出可愛的花朵～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好期待能栽培喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">在這個時期，<colour id="3" />然然<colour id="65535" />要到不同的島嶼<delay20 />
販賣種子和幼苗，<delay8 /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真辛苦啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，我很喜歡種植稀有的花跟灌木，<delay8 />
所以很感謝他<delay20 />常常到島上來呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要把花朵<delay20 />並排種植，<delay8 />
就有機會開出不同顏色的花喔。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />園藝真是博大精深啊～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既然是難得的地球日，<delay20 />
把花摘下來<delay8 />當作髮飾，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />或是裝飾在房間裡都很不錯呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我們一直都把島上的自然環境<delay8 />
視為理所當然，<delay20 />多虧有了地球日，<delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />才能讓我們重新關注環境，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>